::—[[Qur'aan]], [[suurad]]a [[3]]aad ([[Suuratul Al Cimraan]] (ﺁﻝ ﻋﻤﺮﺍﻥ) "[[Qoyskii Cimraan]]"),
[aayad]]a [[33]]aad<ref>"[[Qur'aan]], [[suurad]]a [[3]]aad ([[Suuratul Al Cimraan]] (ﺁﻝ ﻋﻤﺮﺍﻥ) "[[Qoyskii Cimraan]]"),
